campaign_rdb.resp_query_desc_2:
SMS Query Condition: Eg. me myid myanswer
<ul><li>me - This is the keyword (index 0)</li><li>myid - This is the FIRST content (index 1)</li><li>myanswer - This is the SECOND content (index 2)</li></ul>
To select a record based on the id, the SQL query should be set as following:&#013;
<i><b>Select score from mytable where id='xxFIELD_1xx';</b></i>&#013;&#013;
To update the answer with user mobile number and received date(yyyy/mm/dd hh:mm:ss), the SQL query should be as following:&#013;
<i><b>Update mytable set answer='xxFIELD_2xx', mobile_number='xxMOBILExx', received_date='xxRECEIVED_DATExx' where id='xxFIELD_1xx';</b></i>
